message: /* Ukraine is Central European country editing needed to be allowed */
According to opinion already accepted in Wikipedia Europe divisions are disputed. For example look at Switzerland article. Ukraine has arguments to be named Central European.

It was accepted view in Wikipedia that Europe divisions are vogue. For example look at Switzerland which was represented as bot Western and Central European country and look reference explanation. Ukraine has arguments to be named a Central European.
